2. NO REBRANDING AS YOUR OWN
   You may not claim authorship of the original Trainfitter code, UI, or
   security scanner. Redistributing under a different author name without
   credit to SellingVika is prohibited.

3. FORKS MUST BE CLEARLY DISTINCT
   If you fork or create a derivative work:
     - Keep the "Made by SellingVika." header intact.
     - Add your own authorship line AFTER the original.
     - Use a distinct name for your fork (not "Trainfitter").
     - Link back to the original repository in your README.

4. NO UNAUTHORIZED COMMERCIAL USE
   You may not sell the original Trainfitter, nor modified versions of it,
